    c3= 6: c5 in [ 4, 12], min a1 = 10 (or +1 if c7=1), a2=0 rate: 85/275 = 31%
    c3= 7: c5 in [ 7, 14], min a1 = 14 (or +1 if c7=1), a2=0 rate: 44/283 = 16%
    c3= 8: c5 in [ 6, 17], min a1 = 14 (or +1 if c7=1), a2=0 rate: 49/412 = 12%
    c3= 9: c5 in [12, 21], min a1 = 21 (or +1 if c7=1), a2=0 rate: 7/406 = 2%
    c3=10: c5 in [14, 22], min a1 = 24 (or +1 if c7=1), a2=0 rate: 7/530 = 1%
